<p><inline-graphic xlink:href="10.1177_0020294013481703-img1.tif"/></p>
<p>The Institute is delighted to announce that Belcom Cables Ltd has joined the Companion Company Scheme:</p>
<p>Belcom was founded in 1992 to supply control and communication cables to industry. Today, they are the stockholder and distributor of industrial automation cables and have achieved a strong team of professionals with proven industry experience.</p>
<p>Their company mindset is open to every possibility when selecting the cable performance required to complete a project successfully. This could mean a brand new cable design or a radical adaptation of existing designs, or as often happens, a cable straight from their stock to fulfil the necessary requirements.</p>
<p>Based next to London Stansted Airport, Belcom has a heavy commitment to stock holding for UK next day delivery and efficient worldwide delivery. Their approved manufacturing partners, primarily in Europe and North America, are carefully selected to guarantee their supplies of quality-assured and third party–verified cables.</p>
